data.description: This house was just professionally deep cleaned!  Inquire immediately on how you lock up this house risk-free. Discover luxury living in this exquisite three-level home, nestled in a prime location just moments away from vibrant entertainment, chic shopping, and gourmet restaurants. The home is located in a very quiet, friendly and well-maintained neighborhood. This beautifully maintained residence boasts a versatile basement with an in-law suite, complete with its own separate entrance, ensuring privacy and comfort for guests or extended family. Step outside to find your personal oasis: stunning custom built above-ground pool and spa that cost $120,000, perfect for relaxation or hosting memorable gatherings. Renovations add a modern touch, making this home not just a living space, but a statement of elegance and convenience. Welcome to your dream home, where luxury meets lifestyle." A list of special features and upgrades is available by request.
